title: Fresno Community Choir
caption: November 20th
description: The Fresno Community Chorus will be performing the Brahms' German Requiem next Sunday accompanied by full orchestra. This is an excellent opportunity for students in Musicianship IV, III, or freshmen and sophomores to glimpse the masterful work of Brahms (also, performed by one of UHS's very own previous founders: Dr. Brad Huff). Tickets are available at https://fresnocommunitychorus.org/tickets/ and there should be a discounted price for students. Contact fresnocommunitychorus@gmail.com.

title: Thanksgiving Break
caption: November 23rd-25th
description: I hope everyone has a wonderful Thanksgiving Break. The semester is wrapping up so stay strong. Take this time to relax and finish off these last three weeks! Take care. - Kaden :)
